                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; first words (headings or parts of headings) of constituent texts; directives for the ministers; word ʾǝgäle in supplication formulas; some interlineal musical signs; most of the abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
&#xD;
